                            <comment id="492535" author="bzzz" created="Mon, 6 Apr 2026 17:51:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;we discussed &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17536&quot; title=&quot;dentry duplication can break rename checks in VFS&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17536&quot;&gt;LU-17536&lt;/a&gt; with James and if I remember correctly he said that his &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11501&quot; title=&quot;use the dcache properly with .lustre/fid&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11501&quot;&gt;LU-11501&lt;/a&gt; should fix this problem. can be wrong though - it was long ago.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
